	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p><hi rend="underline"><add>Yiddish</add></hi></p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; <date>Monday</date>&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><date>25th of Sivan&#40;June&#41; 1862</date>.</p>
				<p>To my dear friend&#44; <addressee>Lippman Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Friend&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">God is my help&#44; the Creator of heaven&#44; and He<lb/>&#42; who made the land from the formless void&#44; that I<lb/> have heard no voice which aroused me against my<lb/> friend. Is this just and right&#63;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">For several months past I have been more<lb/> upset than ever because of the unpleasant ex<lb/>perience which I had through <persName>Ettinger</persName>. The order<lb/> of these sad events through which I am delayed<lb/> in completing my work&#44; or to undertake any&#45;<lb/>thing new&#44; so as to be able to support myself upset<lb/> and bewilder me. &#8220;A man is born for trouble&#8221;.&#42;<lb/> But not for this kind of trouble. I deal with<lb/> general and Jewish books and stationary&#44; but<lb/> the <add>blank</add> have forsaken me.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">And now&#44; dear friend&#44; after long pain<lb/> and delay &#40;for my prayer has been heard&#41; I am<lb/> almost finished with the work in Hebrew &#8220;Your Nati<add>&#63;</add> me<lb/> Hagvei <add>&#63;</add> Ha&#45;Selang<add>&#63;</add>&#8221; &#40;My dove from the nests of the Rock&#41;<lb/> Cantides 214<lb/> Now&#44; I beg of you to let me know whether I ought<lb/> to let it be copied for me in square letters&#44; that<lb/> would cost too much. Rashi script would cost less<lb/> It were even better if you or someone else over</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)">&#42;From <persName>Job</persName></p>
				<p>&#42; This first sentence is in</p>
				<p>Hebrew.  This is the best I</p>
				<p>can do with it.<lb/> <persName>S. G.</persName></p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>there could read my writing. The cost is the most<lb/> important consideration for me at present.<lb/> That is why I expect to go there next week in<lb/> order to talk the matter over personally. It is<lb/> possible to say things verbally which cannot be<lb/> said in writing.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Also&#44; please let me know who is <persName>Jacob<lb/> Friedman</persName>. He says that he knows me. I&#44;<lb/> however cannot recall him. Could he pos&#45;<lb/>sibly be from <placeName>Hamburg</placeName>&#63; Also let me<lb/> know whether he can be trusted with holiday<lb/> prayer&#45;books. Expecting your immediate<lb/> reply&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Your friend&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Office 429 Broadway</placeName>.</p>
		</body>
